OL,3,CDeputy Prime Minister calls for
OL,4,Cjustice after Grenfell Inquiry
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police and Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service must act "as
OL,8,Fquickly as possible" over the Grenfell
OL,9,FTower blaze, the Deputy Prime Minister
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FAngela Rayner faced questions from
OL,13,Fbroadcasters on Thursday 6 September
OL,14,Fabout the next steps ministers will
OL,15,Ftake following the end of the inquiry
OL,16,Finto the 2017 tower block fire.
