OL,3,CDeputy Prime Minister calls for
OL,4,Cjustice after Grenfell Inquiry
OL,6,FThe Housing Secretary's appearance on
OL,7,Fthe airwaves comes after Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer issued a state apology for a
OL,9,Fdisaster he said should never have
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister said the Government
OL,13,Fwill look at all 58 of the inquiry's
OL,14,Frecommendations "in detail".
OL,16,FMs Rayner told Times Radio "justice
OL,17,Fdelayed is justice denied".
OL,19,F"This is an incredibly complex
OL,20,Finvestigation," she said.
OL,26,@vD@QOUvD@[O]xD@\OUyD@ZO]{D@AOU|D@OO]
