OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F404A1725548314
OL,3,CDeputy Prime Minister calls for
OL,4,Cjustice after Grenfell Inquiry
OL,6,F"And as this is seven years on, and
OL,7,Fthe phase two report is out, and it's
OL,8,Fincredibly detailed, there's
OL,9,Fconsiderable volumes to go through,
OL,10,Fand we will do everything we can to
OL,11,Fsupport the Met Police and the CPS to
OL,12,Fensure that they can bring their
OL,13,Ffindings and take their action forward
OL,14,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,16,F"Because, as many of the survivors and
OL,17,Fthe families of the victims have
OL,18,Fsaid... justice delayed, is justice
OL,19,Fdenied, and I absolutely agree that
OL,20,Fthis has to come as quickly as
OL,21,Fpossible."
