OL,3,CDeputy Prime Minister calls for
OL,4,Cjustice after Grenfell Inquiry
OL,6,F"At the moment, there's #5 billion
OL,7,Fthat's available for remediation, so I
OL,8,Fdon't accept that the money's not
OL,9,Fthere," she said.
OL,11,F"And these companies, the people that
OL,12,Fown these buildings, have financial
OL,13,Fresources as well.
OL,15,F"I don't accept that there is not the
OL,16,Fmoney to do this remediation."
OL,18,FShe said there were sometimes "very
OL,19,Fcomplex" ownership structures for the
OL,20,Fbuildings.
