OL,6,F"Some are owned offshore, and I'm
OL,7,Flooking at that now and how we can
OL,8,Fcontinue to really hold these building
OL,9,Fowners to account, to make sure that
OL,10,Fthey do the work.
OL,12,F"There's no excuse to not do this work
OL,13,Fnow."
OL,15,FMs Rayner also acknowledged some
OL,16,Fpeople still live in buildings that
OL,17,Fmight not be safe.
