OL,3,CDeputy Prime Minister calls for
OL,4,Cjustice after Grenfell Inquiry
OL,6,F"All buildings in the UK could have a
OL,7,Ffailure of some sort. I can't
OL,8,Fguarantee 100% that every building in
OL,9,Fthe UK is going to be 100% safe," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"But what I can say is that measures
OL,13,Fhave been taken to ensure that there
OL,14,Fare fire evacuation procedures, that
OL,15,Fwhere there is a waking watch that's
OL,16,Frequired, that there is a process with
OL,17,Fthe fire brigade to ensure that people
OL,18,Fare safe."
