OL,6,FThe tower block was covered in
OL,7,Fcombustible products because of the
OL,8,F"systematic dishonesty" of firms who
OL,9,Fmade and sold the cladding and
OL,10,Finsulation, he added, with cladding
OL,11,Fcompany Arconic and insulation firms
OL,12,FKingspan and Celotex coming in for
OL,13,Fparticularly heavy criticism.
