OL,6,FSir Keir told Parliament all firms
OL,7,Ffound by the inquiry to be part of the
OL,8,F"horrific failings" will be written to
OL,9,F"as the first step" to stopping them
OL,10,Fbeing awarded such contracts.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has also said it is
OL,13,F"imperative that there is full
OL,14,Faccountability" for what happened
OL,15,F"including through the criminal
OL,16,Fjustice process".
